71
00:03:17,260 --> 00:03:18,130
Les autres,

72
00:03:19,170 --> 00:03:20,630
tuez-les tous.

73
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:23,470
Chef de clan,

74
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:24,760
rassurez-vous.

75
