Quatre. Cinq. Six.

78
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,180
Venir.

79
00:04:24,380 --> 00:04:25,420
Le prochain.

80
00:04:27,340 --> 00:04:28,920
Vous avez des compétences.

81
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:31,050
